txt.en: Orcs can be found within Harlond\n\nYou should defeat Orcs within Harlond.
Aragorn will need the port of the Harlond cleared if he and his men are to make landfall with haste.
'Many Orcs await orders in the Harlond. You should defeat any Orcs in the port if Aragorn and his men are to make landfall with haste.'
Orcs can be found within the Harlond.\n\nYou should defeat Orcs within the Harlond.
